Linear Regression:
1. based upon the variance between two columns we predict the outcome or prediction or forecast. 

2. Supervised algorithm

3. It can work with single column and also with multiple column 

3.1 Columns are categorised as X and Y 

    3.1.1 x = data or feature data or independent data
    3.1.2 y = data or target data or dependent data

4. As a developer we will be deciding or by experience we will know what should be our x and what should be our y. 

5. Since the name tells "Regression" output or target will be "Continuous" data

5.1 Input or X  or Feature Data can be continuous or regression. 

